txt.en: 'Volume III, Book 6, eh? This is the one with that crazy dream in it! Are you sure you want to skip it?\n\n'I guess you know what you're doing. If you want to complete Volume III Book 6 of the Epic quest, you'll be all set once you complete this quest.'
'You know what? Complete this quest and you'll have Volume III Book 6 of the Epic quest completed.'
Completion of this quest will flag your character has having completed all the quests in Book 6 of the Epic quest series of Volume III.
